javaValidation.Validation

Class SingleLineError

  • java.lang.Object
    • javaValidation.Validation.SingleLineError

  • public class SingleLineError
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds information about an error that exists on a single line within a java file. It holds whether the error can be underlined, the underline bounds, the line number, the type of error, and the error message. Created on 4/19/16.
